    'This will display notifications when new messages are posted in your shop.' => 'Ini akan menampilkan pemberitahuan ketika pesan baru ter-posting pada toko Anda.',
    'PrestaShop is not responsible for your database, its backups and/or recovery.' => 'PrestaShop tidak bertanggung jawab atas database Anda, file Backup, dan proses restore maupun datanya.',
    'How to restore a database backup in 10 easy steps:' => 'Bagaimana melakukan restore database dari backup dalam 10 langkah mudah:',
    'Set "Enable Shop" to "No" in the "Maintenance" page under the "Preferences" menu.' => 'Set "Enable Shop" ke "No di halaman "Maintenance" dibawah menu "Preferences".',
    'Download the backup from the list below or from your FTP server (in the folder "admin/backups").' => 'Ambil Backup dari daftar di bawah atau melalui FTP  (dalam folder "admin/backups").',
    'Check the backup integrity: Look for errors, incomplete file, etc... Be sure to verify all of your data.' => 'Memeriksa integritas backup: mencari kesalahan, file tidak lengkap. Verifikasi data.',
    'Please ask your hosting provider for "phpMyAdmin" access to your database.' => 'Minta penyedia hosting Anda untuk memberikan akseske  "phpMyAdmin" agar Anda dapat mengakses database Anda',
    'Connect to "phpMyAdmin" and select your current database.' => 'Gunakan "phpMyAdmin" dan pilih database yang Anda gunakan.',
    'Unless you enabled the "Drop existing tables" option, you must delete all tables from your current database.' => 'Kecuali Anda mengaktifkan "Hapus tabel yang ada", Anda harus menghapus semua tabel dari database Anda secara manual.',
    'At the top of the screen, please select the "Import" tab' => 'Pada layar atas, pilih tab "Import"',
    'Click on the "Browse" button and select the backup file from your hard drive.' => 'Klik pada tombol "Browse ..." tombol dan pilih Backup file dari hard drive Anda',
    'If your backup file exceeds this limit, contact your hosting provider for assistance. ' => 'Jika berkas rekam cadang melampaui batas ini, hubungi penyedia jasa inang (host) Anda untuk bantuan. ',
